<DocsPageTitle>
    FilePicker component
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    Customized, cross-browser consistent, enchanced file input control that supports single file and multiple files upload.
    Provides extra functionality, listing and detailing files, providing clear and upload buttons and inbuilt progress.
</DocsPageParagraph>

